        <h2>
            陔馀丛考（全三册）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5453737">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5453737/" class="title-link">装帧是真心差</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5453737"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4600677/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4600677-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4600677/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">保卫江安高维岳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-04"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-04 19:36:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5453737_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作为学术笔记，出版的时候字可以大些，哪怕书厚一点。这价钱都够得上精装本了。三册书，放哪显得单薄，怎么也不觉着是这个价。内容没怎么排过版，感觉是缩在那里的，这还不如直接影印呢。书是好书，如果想买，建议试试上海古籍出版社的。该版本还有注释，是精装本。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5453737_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5453737_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
